html.content:
%%[var @Name, @Birthdate, @dayNumber, @monthFullName, @gender,@Email, @lookupValue, @Favourite, @customMessage Set @Name = Name Set @Birthdate = Birthdate Set @dayNumber=FormatDate(@Birthdate,"dd") Set @monthFullName = FormatDate(@Birthdate,"MMMM") set @gender = AttributeValue("Gender") Set @Email = Email Set @Favourite = Lookup("{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/95119bf6-119e-ed11-b84e-48df37d1deb7/data/name}}","item","Email",@Email) if @gender=="female" then set @customMessage="Female Customer" set @imageLink="https://image.s7.sfmc-content.com/lib/fe8d13737467037570/m/1/1d378179-04e1-413c-81d2-292f373f02b7.jpg" elseif @gender=="male" then set @customMessage="Male Customer" set @imageLink="https://image.s7.sfmc-content.com/lib/fe8d13737467037570/m/1/844790d0-c54d-48b6-b950-ae220888b7d2.jpg" endif ]%%

Dear %%=v(@Name)=%%, %%=v(@dayNumber)=%% of %%=v(@monthFullName)=%% is so special in your life and for us as we are celebrating your birthday.
Wishing You many more happy returns of the day.
Your favourite item is %%=v(@Favourite)=%%.
Click below to have your birthday gift as one of our top %%=v(@customMessage)=%%.

activities.name: Update Email Sent and Voucher Redeem

data.name: Birthday_campaign_favourite_items_new
data.queryText:
SELECT  a.Customer_Id,
        a.Name,
        a.Birthdate,
        a.Email,
        a.Gender,
        b.Item
    FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/e8235139-49a2-ed11-b84e-48df37d1deb7/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/e8235139-49a2-ed11-b84e-48df37d1deb7/data/name}}] a
    LEFT JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b856063-49a2-ed11-b84e-48df37d1deb7/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/7b856063-49a2-ed11-b84e-48df37d1deb7/data/name}}] b
    ON a.Item_Purchased=b.Id

data.name: Birthday_Sfmc_Customer_Data_Refresh
data.queryText:
SELECT  Customer_Id,
        Name,
        Birthdate,
        Email,
        Gender,
        Optin,
        Item_Purchased
    FROM {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/a6f8a370-c41f-ee11-b859-48df37d1da95/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/a6f8a370-c41f-ee11-b859-48df37d1da95/data/name}}]
